# National Bank of India - Banking System

## Features
- Secure user authentication with PIN protection
- Complete transaction processing (deposits, withdrawals, transfers)
- Account management and PIN change functionality
- Mini statement generation
- Robust error handling and data validation

## Technical Stack
- Java 8+
- MySQL Database
- Swing for UI

## Setup Instructions

### Database Configuration
1. Create MySQL database:
   ```sql
   CREATE DATABASE bankmanagementsystem;
